functional_data.summary: The M1TTR meganuclease targets a site in exon 1 within the TTR gene.

variants.additional_notes: The study involved rhesus macaques as models for TTR gene editing.
key_quotes: The most common mutation (V30M) is associated with polyneuropathy in ATTR patients.

extraction_metadata.notes: Extracted data was primarily from the main text with no additional tables containing variant information.
